Release 2 - UPDATE
- Support for 32 players
- More Cover
- Fixed Cubemap Issues

Need a stylish arena for your gun game server? Here is the answer, lots of combat options, two floors for intricate gunnery scenarios. The map is optimized for computers of all calibers. Realistic lighting and texturing can be achieved without loss of performance.
